== Variables ==
There are many variables available in make.conf, and as such, only the most commonly used are explained in detail here. For more information, and the full list of variables, consult the make.conf manpage.

{{Note|Different configurations will require different variables to be set up. Do not treat the following as a definitive list of the most important}}

=== CFLAGS / CXXFLAGS ===
Compilation flags.
=== CHOST ===
Compiler. Don't change this lightly. See http://www.gentoo.org/doc/en/change-chost.xml
=== GENTOO_MIRRORS ===
Mirror locations
=== INPUT_DEVICES ===
Input devices
=== LINGUAS ===
Languages
=== MAKEOPTS ===
Makefile opts
=== PORTDIR_OVERLAY ===
Local overlays
=== USE ===
Use flags
=== VIDEO_CARDS ===
Video cards

